messages.message:
Patch Set 2:

@Erno: I disagree about the "services which consume" section.  To make this easy for operators, we want to use the same template for the help text, both within Glance and across projects.  With that section missing, an operator will be wondering: is this the only service that consumes this option, or did someone neglect to make the list?  So this provides a positive assertion that, yes, this is the only consumer.

I agree that it's kind of redundant, but I think it makes sense to leave it in from a broad-picture perspective.
